 "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1974-12-22"},"text":"Dec. 22, 1974","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/88/1724"},"text":"88 Stat. 1724","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to chapter 27 (§ 2601 et seq.) of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s2601"},"text":"section 2601 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secure and Fair Enforcement for Mortgage Licensing Act of 2008, referred to in subsec. (b)(7), is title V of div. A of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/289"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–289","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2008-07-30"},"text":"July 30, 2008","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/122/2810"},"text":"122 Stat. 2810","children":[],"tail":", also known as the S.A.F.E. Mortgage Licensing Act of 2008, which is classified generally to chapter 51 (§ 5101 et seq.) of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s5101"},"text":"section 5101 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Interstate Land Sales Full Disclosure Act, referred to in subsec. (b)(7), is title XIV of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/90/448"},"text":"Pub. L. 90–448","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1968-08-01"},"text":"Aug. 1, 1968","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/82/590"},"text":"82 Stat. 590","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to chapter 42 (§ 1701 et seq.) of Title 15, Commerce and Trade. For complete classification of this title to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1701"},"text":"section 1701 of Title 15","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Federal Credit Union Act, referred to in subsec. (c)(2)(C)(i), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1934-06-26/ch750"},"text":"act June 26, 1934, ch. 750","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/48/1216"},"text":"48 Stat. 1216","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to chapter 14 (§ 1751 et seq.) of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s1751"},"text":"section 1751 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Bank Service Company Act, referred to in subsec. (c)(2)(C)(iii), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/856"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–856","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1962-10-23"},"text":"Oct. 23, 1962","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/76/1132"},"text":"76 Stat. 1132","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to chapter 18 (§ 1861 et seq.) of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s1861"},"text":"section 1861 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"iddd7921f6-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDate","id":"iddd7921f7-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Part effective 1 day after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{